# #Misfits Add - Entrenching tool and barricade construction locale strings.

## Dig
entrenching-dig-novacancy = You can't dig here — the ground isn't suitable.
entrenching-dig-start = You start digging into the earth...
entrenching-dig-finish = You dig up { $count } empty sandbags.

## Fill
entrenching-fill-novacancy = You can't fill sandbags here — the ground isn't suitable.
entrenching-fill-start = You start filling the sandbag with soil...
entrenching-fill-finish = You fill the sandbag.

## Build
entrenching-build-novacancy = You can't build a barricade here.
entrenching-build-notenough = You need at least { $required } full sandbags to build a barricade.
entrenching-build-start = You start stacking sandbags...
entrenching-build-finish = You assemble the barricade.

## Dismantle
entrenching-dismantle-start = You start dismantling the barricade...
entrenching-dismantle-finish = You dismantle the barricade and recover the sandbags.
